social_posts.post_text: This year been pretty crazy… one of the best yet. Sold thousands of tacos with @hughshotbowls … went on tour with @girltalk_verified … played Coachella twice with @isaiahrashad … performed at my aunts 60th bday … but most importantly I learned that if i stay ready my expectations will be surpassed cuz Big God got plans for me I could never imagine! Couldn’t fit all the clips I wanted into this 1:30 highlight reel but y’all get the point 🙏🏾
Final two shows this Friday and Saturday to conclude my touring for the year with @girltalk_verified in St Petersburg and Ft Lauderdale FL!
Smooth Sunday

It’s Mogul Monday! Happy Holidaze y’all! Shit done changed for the better 💙

I remember performing in front of 5 ppl at my first show when I was 17 at Swing House studio that used to be on Formosa and Willoughby. Still on the same mission all these years later. Had my best year in rap yet. Got to go all around the country and get paid to perform my shit at some of the most legendary venues. Still got a few cities I ain’t touch yet and even more I can’t wait to get back to. I know some ngs hated I made the food pop. I’m 7 albums deep on DSPs, that’s over 6 hours of music and even more to come. Remember when I couldn’t get in now ain’t a place I can’t go. I show the crowd in my performance videos cuz I want y’all to see what’s really going on. I know it’s a lot of talk about who’s the best and who got the most but who’s having the most fun with this shit?? A lot of my homies lost the fun part and I’m happy to say it’s still fun for me like it was when me and Domo was rapping in the garage. We used to record on a 4 track tape machine at Bo’s house when we were 12 just happy to hear ourselves on a track. Hope y’all enjoy what I release in 2023 as much as I enjoyed the experiences that inspired me to make it. More music and food. Might open a restaurant??? It’ll happen when the time is right 💙
More wholesome content for your Holidays with my bros… all my homies doing good
I resisted the Xmas Gumbo think I might buy myself something nice today
Coachella Wtfffff!!! 2022 was the year we made dreams into reality. Still riding this high into the new year
Have fun!

It’s amazing how far your two feet can take you. I wasn’t sure what this month long trip to Germany would hold for me. Of course I knew I had shows to play and studio sessions scheduled but there’s always some level of  uncertainty when you leave the comfort of your home for so long. I had an amazing time and was treated with so much kindness and respect I almost didn’t want to leave. From Hamburg to Frankfurt to Berlin and back. All independent with the help of friends like @r3dchild @iamnobodi @na_tothe_om @famara_kassama making sure I’m good out there. I ate great everyday, enjoyed nature, made new friends, danced a lot, rapped even more, and most of all had fun. Album otw.
